description: This is the entry point file for a React-based frontend application. It sets up the React DOM rendering process, attaches the root component 'App' to the DOM element with id 'root', and applies React's strict mode for highlighting potential issues.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components in the DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
